    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I'm parting with this absolute gem, and let me tell you, it's basically perfect. It looks and drives like it just came off the showroom floor\u2014no scratches, no dings, and the interior is spotless. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows! If you're looking for a car that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself. You're going to love it!",
