    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, recently serviced with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and VAC Motorsports rod bearings to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The subframe has been professionally reinforced, addressing the chassis's primary weak point. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the original N\u00fcrburgring-tuned kinematics. Finished in Carbon Black with a flawless Cinnamon Nappa leather interior, this vehicle exhibits zero oil seepage and a clean DME report with no over-rev history. A true turn-key collector piece for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 44500.0,
