    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, museum-grade example that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, seeing pavement only on dry, sunny weekends. The exterior paint retains its factory depth and brilliance, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate controls, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, folder-thick service history with all scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified specialists. The engine bay is detailed to a mirror finish, and the undercarriage is as clean as the topside. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-quality investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection without compromise.",
